title: Maya Jane Coles Essential Mix #1004 2013.05.04 (NO VOICEOVER)
description:
Fans of Maya Jane Coles got an Easter egg right after her second essential mix dropped via soundcloud: A wav copy of the mix with no voiceover by Pete Tong. I don't know how long it was up but it's now an MP3 on SC. If you wanted hands-down the best copy, this is it.

Share and Enjoy

Maya Jane Coles Essential Mix #1004 May 4, 2013


encoded at -8 compression (best)
